==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Colt pistol
<hw>Colt pistol</hw>. <fld>(Firearms)</fld> <def>A self-loading or
semi-automatic pistol with removable magazine in the handle holding
seven cartridges. The recoil extracts and ejects the empty cartridge
case, and reloads ready for another shot. Called also <altname>Browning
pistol</altname>, <altname>Colt-Browning pistol</altname>,
<altname>automatic pistol</altname> and
<altname>automatic</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Colt revolver</ent>⟦br⟧
